things we do as managers, right?

7
00:00:20.390 --> 00:00:22.550
We need to forecast future
financial performance,

8
00:00:22.550 --> 00:00:26.460
but if you think about it, right,
the actions you take are nonfinancials.

9
00:00:26.460 --> 00:00:28.150
Am I going to invest money in R&D?

10
00:00:28.150 --> 00:00:29.560
Am I going to do a marketing initiative?

11
