if we take these nonfinancial actions,

14
00:00:36.157 --> 00:00:39.851
how do we think that's ultimately going to
impact our financial performance?

15
00:00:39.851 --> 00:00:43.220
So we need to know this for
forecasting future cash flows.

16
00:00:43.220 --> 00:00:46.980
We need to know when we're going to choose
projects of the many choices I have

17
00:00:46.980 --> 00:00:48.320
