18
00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:51.150
Do I focus on improving
customer satisfaction, or

19
00:00:51.150 --> 00:00:53.300
do I focus on improving
the quality of my product?

20
00:00:53.300 --> 00:00:54.810
Well, both of those are nonfinancial.

21
00:00:54.810 --> 00:00:58.780
What I want to know is, when I
improve this nonfinancial dimension,

22
00:00:58.780 --> 00:01:02.080
what's the ultimate impact going to
be on my financial performance?

23
00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:04.280
And obviously one of the big
reasons we care about this,

24
00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:07.230
is you're going to get evaluated
on this for performance measures.

25
00:01:07.230 --> 00:01:09.696
A lot of companies been putting
in dashboards and scorecards,

26
00:01:09.696 --> 00:01:11.844
they're everywhere,
for-profit, non-profit.

27
00:01:11.844 --> 00:01:15.355
The idea there is a lot of the actions
that you take as a manager,

28
00:01:15.355 --> 00:01:19.481
do not show up in short term financial
results for a while, there is a lag.

29
00:01:19.481 --> 00:01:20.066
Or even worse,

30
00:01:20.066 --> 00:01:23.050
