54
00:02:34.750 --> 00:02:37.310
Then how do I pick the targets for these?

55
00:02:37.310 --> 00:02:38.720
How happy do I want my employees?

56
00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:40.751
What kind of employee turnover do I want?

57
