in leading into financials.

71
00:03:25.040 --> 00:03:26.640
One, what should we be measuring?

72
00:03:27.660 --> 00:03:29.820
I don't have any problem coming
up with nonfinancial measures,

73
00:03:29.820 --> 00:03:33.920
we could sit around the table here, in 15
minutes, we could come up with hundreds.

74
00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:38.030
What I want to know is, of those
hundreds of nonfinancial measures, which

75
00:03:38.030 --> 00:03:42.290
one of those when they move up and down,
actually tell me something I care about?

76
00:03:42.290 --> 00:03:44.790
It's not just a matter
of I want nonfinancials.

77
00:03:44.790 --> 00:03:48.340
What we want are, what are the key
drivers of financial success?

78
00:03:48.340 --> 00:03:50.970
Now drivers is a very important word here.

79
00:03:50.970 --> 00:03:54.170
That means,
when a manager actually takes this action,

80
00:03:54.170 --> 00:03:58.350
it actually leads to this thing I
care about on the other side on this.

81
00:03:58.350 --> 00:04:00.736
And that's what we want to get
with predictive analytics,

82
00:04:00.736 --> 00:04:02.827
is I want to predict this,
based on these actions,

83
00:04:02.827 --> 00:04:04.984
what is going to drive future
financial performance?

84
00:04:04.984 --> 00:04:07.318
So that's the first thing is
what are we going to measure?

85
00:04:07.318 --> 00:04:09.925
The next thing we have to worry about is,
how do I rank or

86
00:04:09.925 --> 00:04:13.000
weight these things when I have
various financial measures?

87
00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:16.380
Now some of your companies have
something called a balance scorecard.

88
00:04:16.380 --> 00:04:19.550
And with the balance scorecard
you have financial measures, but

89
00:04:19.550 --> 00:04:21.990
you also have customer measures.

90
00:04:21.990 --> 00:04:24.650
You have operations or
productivity measures, and

91
00:04:24.650 --> 00:04:26.840
you have what are called learning and
growth measures.

92
00:04:26.840 --> 00:04:28.160
Well, that's great, so

93
00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:32.181
