00:04:32.181 --> 00:04:36.699
How do I know how to rank or weight these
varies, do I really want to spend more

95
00:04:36.699 --> 00:04:40.658
time on improving quality or
improving customer satisfaction?

96
00:04:40.658 --> 00:04:44.289
It's really easy to rank financial
numbers, because they're all in currency,

97
00:04:44.289 --> 00:04:46.340
they're in a common denominator.

98
00:04:46.340 --> 00:04:50.060
The problem with nonfinancial measures is,
they're not in a common denominator.

99
00:04:50.060 --> 00:04:53.325
Some are in percentages,
some are in weight, some are in time,

100
00:04:53.325 --> 00:04:55.010
they could be in anything.

101
00:04:55.010 --> 00:04:58.670
How do I combine those or
